fields.content: Thank You so much for being such a fantastic teacher! I’ve loved every minute and will really miss regular lessons! You’ve really made me love playing the piano.

Emy has been helping our daughter (6) with general tuition Viola for about three months. She is punctual, polite and has quickly established an excellent rapport with our child. We have been very impressed with what we have seen so far.
Amy taught my son for a couple of years and was always professional, kind and encouraging - I highly recommend her.
